BEST SOLUTION USING BINOMIAL FORMULA AND COMBINATIONS APPROACH
WATCH STRIVER EXPLAINATION
TC : O(n-1) or O(m-1) SC : O(1)
PLEASE UPVOTE

 int uniquePaths(int m, int n) {
        int N = m+n-2;
        int r = m-1;
        double res = 1;
        for(int i=1;i<=r;i++)
            res=res*(N-r+i)/i;
        return(int)res;
    }
Better then DP and Recursive approach
